        "subject": "LU-6202 libcfs: fixed buffer overflow in IOC_LIBCFS_MARK_DEBUG",
        "message": "LU-6202 libcfs: fixed buffer overflow in IOC_LIBCFS_MARK_DEBUG\n\nIf this ioctl is called with data->ioc_inllen1 == 0, we\ndereference ioc_inlbuf1, which hasn't been validated,\nand index *before* the pointer, then create a debug message\nwith all the bytes *after* the pointer until the first nul.\nThis could create a debug message from an arbitrarily large\namount of garbage.\n\nChange-Id: I60714328182217b641e4df21bb8fd6ca307a8847\nSigned-off-by: NeilBrown <neilb@suse.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
